title: Readout of Vice President Biden's Call with Kurdistan Regional President Massoud Barzani | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Vice President


For Immediate Release
December 16, 2010

 



Readout of Vice President Biden's Call with Kurdistan Regional President Massoud Barzani





	The Vice President spoke to Kurdistan Regional Government President Massoud Barzani today to discuss progress on government formation talks.Â  The Vice President also extended his congratulations to President Barzani on his re-election as Chairman of the Kurdistan Democratic Party.
